{
  "stem": "7832.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The people that were in the experiment with me, I-- the-- the-- the girl that was in the-- in the dungeon, like, next to me, and I was able to touch her, or talk to her.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we didn't see each other, what we looked like while we were there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But when we came out, we were holding on to each other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so we stood next to one another so we can see each other and see who we are.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so they brought her back to-- to Birkenau to the laager [INAUDIBLE], but she wasn't in my barrack.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She was in a different barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- but I knew what she looked like, and she knew what I looked like.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then they took us for experiment again, but then there was only five of us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't know what happened to the other 10, and she was among the five.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So every-- then we went for an experiment where they were injecting some kind of a serum under the nail of our finger and sent us back to the barrack.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then took us back to see what it does and took blood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we found out that they were doing some kind of a virus testing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had an infection going up from my-- that's why my finger is disordered like that, from the injection.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had a red line going up my arm when they sent me back to the barrack, in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- I remembered that-- from school that that means a blood infection.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the way to treat it is to tie it up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, I had nothing to tie it up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I couldn't-- see, I used my one piece of clothing for toilet paper.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
